claim.claim-text:
An agent containing parathyroid hormone (PTH) as the active ingredient for use in the treatment or prevention of osteoporosis in a patient, wherein the PTH containing agent is to be administered once a week in a unit dose of 200 units, and wherein the patient satisfies all of the following conditions (1) through (3):
(1) age 65 years or older;
(2) prevalent bone fractures;
(3) bone density less than 80% of the young adult mean and/or a degree of bone atrophy of I or higher.
